title: [LFT] Mid/ADC
body:
I honestly want to get better at teamwork by working with team... I believe I'm pretty weak at most lanes but there is still room for improvement, so I would like to see if a team or a bunch of people would like to create team. Either way... Magamis is my ign

Mid and ADC have been a strong picks for me this season, but I can go into practicing other lanes, especially jungling.
